title: Most shazamed songs of all time worldwide 2018
summary: This is a bar chart representing Song Titles in the x axis and Number of identifications in millions in the y axis.
The Number of identifications in millions is appeared to be the highest at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and lowest at Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.
Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii has 1.35 times more Number of identifications in millions than Song Titles All of Me by John Legend which is has the lowest.
min_summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Number of identifications in millions for 10 number of Song Titless.
The Number of identifications in millions is appeared to be the highest at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and lowest at Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.
mid_summary: This is a bar chart representing Song Titles in the x axis and Number of identifications in millions in the y axis.
The Number of identifications in millions is appeared to be the highest at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and lowest at Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.

max_summary: This bar chart has 10 columns on the x axis representing Song Titles, and Number of identifications in millions in each Song Titles on the y axis.
The maximum Number of identifications in millions 23.77 is found at Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and the minimum is found at All of Me by John Legend where Song Titles is 17.58.
There is a difference of 6.19 between the maximum Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii and minimum Song Titles All of Me by John Legend.

The Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii has the highest Number of identifications in millions, followed by Somebody That I Used To Know by Gotye feat. Kimbra, and Lean On by Major Lazer Feat. MØ & DJ Snake. Down to the Song Titles All of Me by John Legend which is the lowest.
The Song Titles Wake Me Up by Avicii has 1.15 times more Number of identifications in millions than average.
The Number of identifications in millions is 206.43 if we add up values of all Song Titless.
